      <acqinfo id="aspace_ffc085eccdb4ba03e09496562b393036">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>These items were purchased by the Library in 1983; they had been in the possession of Mrs. A.L. Baldwin, adopted daughter of Horace Waller's son. They supplement and provide supporting detail for the major collection of Waller papers located at Rhodes House Library in Oxford, England.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
